{"tid":523710,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"認真求救，有無人可以俾十萬我或教我點做？","createTime":"2018-01-09T00:03:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-09T11:43:40.000Z","uid":32732,"like":1,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"aedff4a7c083cd371419ea787f4106fd6e621a3f","tid":523710,"uid":32732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T00:03:45.000Z","msg":"我有一位朋友，因為剛同佢老公分居，一個女人無咩錢，無錢無地方住。最慘係佢確診左一期子宮頸癌，開始左電療，但根本唔夠錢，仲差十萬幾。初初個主診醫生都願意收平佢，同等我朋友分期俾，但俾間醫院班pk 管理層發現左，就怪個主診醫做壞規矩，仲要我朋友要一次過俾 先同我朋友做下次醫療。我已經盡幫，但都是唔夠。想試下眾籌幫佢或有無一些社工，專業人士俾點意見。 真心要救命！"},{"pid":"5c41043d0fa10bef59e6f8d01e1a23f0c3d6b6b2","tid":523710,"uid":91647,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T00:06:31.000Z","msg":"網上其實有好多 fund raising website<br />\n真人真事可以試下既<br />\n<br />\n但係覺得巴打你開錯topic"},{"pid":"acb28332b5f8b9e99b00796bafadbf93343d72d0","tid":523710,"uid":91647,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T00:06:58.000Z","msg":"同埋呢個世界重有公營醫院"},{"pid":"c84c01470a44a89996172649fda6b2df66af146d","tid":523710,"uid":19858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T00:08:08.000Z","msg":"搵社署"},{"pid":"7010c69b68749317a7fc663497f81157b4240879","tid":523710,"uid":32732,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"5c41043d0fa10bef59e6f8d01e1a23f0c3d6b6b2","tid":523710,"uid":91647,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T00:06:31.000Z","msg":"網上其實有好多 fund raising website<br />\n真人真事可以試下既<br />\n<br />\n但係覺得巴打你開錯topic"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T00:09:59.000Z","msg":"我都係盲公亂投醫， 真係唔多識 ， 但你所講fund raising 會連咁case 都受的嗎？"},{"pid":"8aae1e392e6df2c744abcb3134b6b824c188b20d","tid":523710,"uid":42283,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T00:10:24.000Z","msg":"冇錢唔去公營醫院？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c63caa28870adbbb47e5c8552a2a4038e24538c","tid":523710,"uid":9924,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T00:12:23.00